Ing '''amapola'''  (''Hibiscus mutabilis''), a '''Confederate rose''' '''cotton rosemallow''' king Ingles, tanaman yang kilala kareng kayang sampaga.  

Mala[[palungpung]] la o lupa lang [[pun dutung]] deng amapola kareng malisangan o malisangan bagyang lugal, oneng mas kalupa yang [[tanaman a pilmihan]] kareng lugal king [[pangulu]] da reti. Malyari lang dobli o tunggal deng sampaga a maki lapad a 4 to 6&nbsp;pulgada; makabuklat lang maputi o rosas, at magi lang malutung malutu karas ning bengi. Maki malutu yang sampaga ing variety o uring 'Rubra'. Keraklan, katabas lang tasa deng tunggal a sampagang bubukadkad. Keraklan, manyampaga la manibat kaleldo anggang kalagas Bloom season usually lasts (''from summer through fall''). Parakalan do deti kapamilatan ning da reng pinutut a sanga (''cuttings''), a pekamalagwang mikakayamut neng mumunang dake ning kasibul (''early spring''), oneng makapamutut para king pamagpatubu anggyang sanung dake ning banwa. Nung e magyelu, miraras yang tas a 15 anggang 18 pie ma marutung ing pun dutung a amapola; nanupata, mas marlas la reng tanamang maki tas a 5 o 6 pie a mala[[palungpung]], a mas dakal sampaga. Taganang mabilis lang dagul teng tanaman a reti.

Kanita, asnong karakal king [[Confederate States of America]] deng amapola, anya ita ing penibatan ning lagyu na king Ingles a '''Confederate rose'''. Kapad na ing deretsu king aslag ning aldo o makasilung bagya, at buri na ing gabun a mataba ampong e mititipun danum.<ref>[http://aggie-horticulture.tamu.edu/southerngarden/hibiscus.html William C. Welch: "Hardy Hibiscus", Texas A&M University]</ref>
